column4: hey, folks. i just tried to get last.fm working with rhythmbox by doing (sudo /etc/init.d/alsa-utils reset) and now my sound doesn't work.
line, mic, mic boost, and IEC958 are muted
i got the wireless to work.. kind of proud of myself
MM is all the way down
